 |f(x,y_1)-f(x,y_2)|=\left|\frac{\partial F}{\partial y}\left(x,\theta y_1+(1-\theta)y_2\right)\right||y_1-y_2|\leqslant M|y_1-y_2|,\text{ for }(x,y_1),(x,y_2)\in R. 
